{"tid":2146240,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"周梓樂離世九個月 有市民悼念期間被發違限聚令告票","createTime":"2020-08-08T12:39:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-08T13:42:20.000Z","uid":21470,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"d4d617a1b3a4fe0085f2475956ee9b4e7237f6ae","tid":2146240,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T12:39:40.000Z","msg":"周梓樂離世九個月 有市民悼念期間被發違限聚令告票<br />\n最後更新時間 2020-08-08 20:29<br />\n<br />\n今天是科大學生周梓樂離世9個月，有市民在他墮樓的將軍澳尚德邨停車場外擺放鮮花悼念。多部警車傍晚起在現場戒備，數十名軍裝警員晚上７時半過後拉起橙帶，圍封擺放鮮花的區域，並截查在場市民，包括記者。最少3名市民被警方以違反限聚令為由，發出定額罰款告票，有市民指，自己只是在場等過馬路，但都被發告票，表示不滿。<br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/local/2351307\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Flocal%2F2351307&d=Ieu1u4uPL9fG%2BDPeYXLiWz632Ab34%2FJQlYP9Mjrnz38%3D&h=4df404b2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/local/2351307</a>"},{"pid":"2e1535da7cc6e1e806f4dda3ac22f2f7785b160c","tid":2146240,"uid":343361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T12:42:59.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8ea852e0305e1190aa69cd434c13a9dc50c87bc8","tid":2146240,"uid":105340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T13:41:29.000Z","msg":"推 無NUMBER可以唔交 等上庭<br />\n你過馬路 咁都比你"},{"pid":"8bde37ae022e854dccf9d5e9483c8120255b890a","tid":2146240,"uid":51621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T13:42:20.000Z","msg":"國際線有任 請每日推Post<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FTwitterHelpBot&d=Ieu1u4uPL9fG%2BDPeYXLiWz632Ab34%2FJQlYP9Mjrnz38%3D&h=6f339344\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot</a>"}]}